# Backend API — must be an address the DEVICE can reach (not "localhost",
# which on a phone/emulator means the device itself).
#   • Android emulator (current): http://10.0.2.2:8080  — alias to this PC's localhost
#   • Physical device on same Wi-Fi: use this PC's LAN IP, e.g. http://192.168.100.4:8080
API_BASE_URL=http://10.0.2.2:8080
